snippet.title: ANNO 1800  GAMESCOM 2018 TRAILER
snippet.description: Lead the Industrial Revolution in ANNO 1800 The path you choose will define your world. Are you an innovator or an exploiter? A conqueror or a liberator? How the world remembers your name is up to you. Build your city and cross the oceans to expand to South America.
